cs.SD, cs.CL, cs.SI, cs.LG, cs.AI 

This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.SD (Sound) as it deals with audio signals and their processing. It could also belong to cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it involves language identification. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.SI (Signal Processing) as it involves processing of audio signals. The use of deep learning tools suggests it could also be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
